choices.text:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for today.  I can't have dairy, garlic, honey, almonds, pistachios, or cashews
Here is your personalized meal plan that excludes the food groups you mentioned:
Breakfast: Avocado smoothie (without actual avocados) and whole grain toast with peanut butter substitute (sunflower seeds mixed with chia seeds).
Lunch: Quino salad (substitute for quino).
Dinner: Lentil stew (lentils without onions or garlic).
